#

Lemon Herb Shrimp with Asparagus

$15.99
350 kcal

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Low-CarbHigh-Protein

Tags:

SeafoodHealthyQuick

Description

Succulent shrimp seared to perfection with a zesty lemon herb sauce, complemented by fresh asparagus for a delightful dish.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp: 1 lb
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Olive oil: 3 tbsp
  • Lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • Fresh parsley: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
